text.section:
An application for a grant shall include:
project plans for the work to be carried out;
a statement listing the personnel employed or to be employed at the residential child care program, including all compensation for personnel services and all other expenses paid or to be paid to the personnel;
all other expenses incurred or to be incurred in operating the residential child care program; and
a statement describing how the residential child care program will provide services in an underserved geographic area of the State, as identified by the Office.
